<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 18:09:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列战事，第 192 天：哈马斯提出基于 41 天休战的提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-192-hamas-presents-proposal-based-on-41-day-truce/0000018e-e2a9-de89-afbf-ffad8e2f0001</link><description>据报道，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡办公室的官员表示，“以色列不能允许如此大规模的袭击”而不做出某种回应。 ■ 哈马斯向调解员发出了围绕 41 天停火的建议。联合国表示，真主党声称对以色列-黎巴嫩边境四名以色列国防军士兵受伤的爆炸事件负责。在战争结束 192 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:53:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-192-hamas-presents-proposal-based-on-41-day-truce/0000018e-e2a9-de89-afbf-ffad8e2f0001</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击后，由于安全局势，易捷航空取消飞往以色列的航班一周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/easyjet-cancels-flights-to-israel-for-a-week-due-to-security-situation-after-irans-attack/0000018e-e251-d9ed-a9ce-fed79da30000</link><description>这家英国廉价航空公司宣布，预计 4 月 21 日（逾越节前一天）之前不会恢复往返以色列的航班</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/easyjet-cancels-flights-to-israel-for-a-week-due-to-security-situation-after-irans-attack/0000018e-e251-d9ed-a9ce-fed79da30000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击后，拜登为内塔尼亚胡提供了另一条生命线，但以色列右翼基地不会接受</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-right-wing-base-wont-let-netanyahu-take-bidens-lifeline-after-the-iran-attack/0000018e-e1ef-d9f8-a7df-e1ff06d40000</link><description>导致哈马斯 10 月 7 日发动袭击的原因正是导致伊朗在周日发射数百枚导弹和无人机的原因：人们认为内塔尼亚胡右翼政府领导下的以色列软弱、分裂，并且与美国关系不好。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:21:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-right-wing-base-wont-let-netanyahu-take-bidens-lifeline-after-the-iran-attack/0000018e-e1ef-d9f8-a7df-e1ff06d40000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击的后果是结束以色列各条战线战争的机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/the-aftermath-of-irans-attack-is-an-opportunity-to-end-israels-wars-on-all-fronts/0000018e-e124-de2f-a5ff-e93eee6d0000</link><description>伊朗明确表示，如果以色列不回应，本轮谈判就结束。希望以色列领导人不会被拖入危险的升级之中</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 15:12:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/the-aftermath-of-irans-attack-is-an-opportunity-to-end-israels-wars-on-all-fronts/0000018e-e124-de2f-a5ff-e93eee6d0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党称其在黎巴嫩和以色列边境附近放置了一枚炸弹，造成四名以色列国防军士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-says-it-planted-a-bomb-on-lebanon-israel-border-wounding-four-idf-soldiers/0000018e-e1ea-d9df-abdf-e7eb72370000</link><description>以色列军队称爆炸发生在黎巴嫩领土数百米处 ■ 以色列国防军称爆炸来源不明，真主党声称对此负责</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 14:28:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-says-it-planted-a-bomb-on-lebanon-israel-border-wounding-four-idf-soldiers/0000018e-e1ea-d9df-abdf-e7eb72370000</guid></item><item><title>抵制“战争的狂喜”：宗教左翼以色列士兵眼中的加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/resisting-the-ecstasy-of-war-gaza-through-the-eyes-of-religious-leftist-israeli-soldiers/0000018e-ce86-d283-a5ee-fe9ff47e0000</link><description>对于宗教左翼分子来说，他们在加沙担任预备役军人期间，围绕军事命令的道德复杂性在他们内部引发了一场独特的战斗——尤其是在目睹与犹太价值观相悖的“可耻行为”时</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/resisting-the-ecstasy-of-war-gaza-through-the-eyes-of-religious-leftist-israeli-soldiers/0000018e-ce86-d283-a5ee-fe9ff47e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯坚持与伊朗结盟对抗以色列，但承认自己在加沙战争中是孤立的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hamas-clings-to-its-alliance-with-iran-but-acknowledges-it-stands-alone-in-the-gaza-war/0000018e-e134-d09b-afff-ef3ded730000</link><description>哈马斯的加沙领导层完全支持伊朗对以色列的袭击，但它也明白，德黑兰几乎不可能采取类似的行动来帮助该组织实现其野心并确保其在战后加沙地带的地位</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:45:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hamas-clings-to-its-alliance-with-iran-but-acknowledges-it-stands-alone-in-the-gaza-war/0000018e-e134-d09b-afff-ef3ded730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队将加沙的一位奶奶与家人分开。她的死将困扰她的子孙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-troops-separated-a-gaza-grandma-from-her-family-her-death-will-haunt-her-descendants/0000018e-e154-dba1-a7df-eb5f1f900000</link><description>以色列士兵射杀了加沙奶奶吗？她是死于饥饿还是口渴，卧床不起，孤身一人吗？她是被浓烟窒息还是被烧死的？</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:32:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-troops-separated-a-gaza-grandma-from-her-family-her-death-will-haunt-her-descendants/0000018e-e154-dba1-a7df-eb5f1f900000</guid></item><item><title>联合国：以色列加沙缓冲区几乎所有建筑物被摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/un-almost-all-buildings-in-israels-buffer-zone-in-gaza-were-destroyed/0000018e-e12a-d09b-afff-ef2f2ccf0000</link><description>据联合国卫星中心称，缓冲区内 90% 的建筑物遭到损坏或摧毁。国际社会认为该项目毁坏了数千座建筑物，可能构成战争罪</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:26:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/un-almost-all-buildings-in-israels-buffer-zone-in-gaza-were-destroyed/0000018e-e12a-d09b-afff-ef2f2ccf0000</guid></item><item><title>“隐藏面粉”：以色列阿拉伯人如何面对伊朗的袭击而大笑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hide-the-flour-how-palestinians-in-israel-laughed-in-the-face-of-irans-attack/0000018e-e12f-d09b-afff-ef2f28110000</link><description>当导弹、火箭和无人机从伊朗飞向以色列时，一些巴勒斯坦人爬上屋顶记录这一事件，而另一些人则通过社交媒体并用幽默作为应对机制</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hide-the-flour-how-palestinians-in-israel-laughed-in-the-face-of-irans-attack/0000018e-e12f-d09b-afff-ef2f28110000</guid></item><item><title>美国报道：伊朗一半弹道导弹失败，以色列空军基地飞机受损；阿联酋与沙特分享情报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/u-s-sources-half-of-iranian-ballistic-missiles-failed-idf-aircraft-damaged/0000018e-e0d0-d7e5-a1fe-e7d1bf3a0000</link><description>美国官员告诉美国广播公司新闻和华尔街日报，五枚弹道导弹击中了南部的内瓦蒂姆空军基地，损坏了一架运输机，四枚弹道导弹击中了另一个基地。在美国压力下，阿联酋和沙特阿拉伯在袭击前分享了伊朗的袭击计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:38:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/u-s-sources-half-of-iranian-ballistic-missiles-failed-idf-aircraft-damaged/0000018e-e0d0-d7e5-a1fe-e7d1bf3a0000</guid></item><item><title>勇敢对抗伊朗的阿拉伯国家不会参与协助以色列的反击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-stood-up-to-iran-wont-be-on-board-to-assist-an-israeli-counterstrike/0000018e-e0df-d4da-a18f-ecfffe8e0000</link><description>约旦、沙特阿拉伯和该地区其他国家都在与美国甚至以色列结盟，以平衡其内部稳定。以色列打击伊朗的前景可能会阻止他们与伊朗结盟</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-stood-up-to-iran-wont-be-on-board-to-assist-an-israeli-counterstrike/0000018e-e0df-d4da-a18f-ecfffe8e0000</guid></item><item><title>威尼斯双年展以色列馆馆长表示，我不是以色列的发言人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-not-israels-spokeswoman-says-curator-of-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-dce6-dab2-a7ae-ddffbf0c0000</link><description>尽管遭到艺术界的强烈反对以及对亲巴勒斯坦抗议者暴力行为的担忧，威尼斯双年展的以色列馆仍将于本周开放。策展人米拉·拉皮多特 (Mira Lapidot) 对艺术家因其民族身份而受到排斥感到愤怒，同时拒绝将自己视为国家的代表</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:40:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-not-israels-spokeswoman-says-curator-of-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-dce6-dab2-a7ae-ddffbf0c0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙停火六周后，哈马斯提议分阶段释放以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hamas-offers-phased-release-of-israeli-hostages-after-six-week-gaza-cease-fire/0000018e-e090-d09b-afff-eebd7b990000</link><description>哈马斯提议分三个阶段释放人质并解除对加沙地带的围困。一名美国高级官员表示，辛瓦尔希望扣押人质，包括年轻妇女、老人和伤员，即使这意味着不会立即停火</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article/.premium/hamas-offers-phased-release-of-israeli-hostages-after-six-week-gaza-cease-fire/0000018e-e090-d09b-afff-eebd7b990000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军主席访问伊朗目标基地，表示以色列将对向以色列领土发射的导弹做出回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article-live/u-s-to-explore-measures-to-hold-iran-accountable-at-the-un/0000018e-df82-d4da-a18f-dfa37abc0000</link><description>哈勒维中将访问内瓦蒂姆空军基地，称伊朗将对导弹发射做出回应 ■ 战时内阁召开数小时会议，讨论应对伊朗袭击的方案 ■ 伊朗外长表示，如果以色列进行报复，德黑兰将做出比以前更强硬的回应 ■白宫：最近几天对加沙的人道主义援助大幅增加 ■ 拜登：美国致力于以色列的安全以及将人质带回家的停火协议</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 02:35:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-15/ty-article-live/u-s-to-explore-measures-to-hold-iran-accountable-at-the-un/0000018e-df82-d4da-a18f-dfa37abc0000</guid></item><item><title>“结盟的机会”或“发狂”：以色列领导人回应伊朗的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/opportunity-for-alliance-or-go-berserk-israels-leaders-respond-to-irans-attack/0000018e-ddf7-d7e5-a1fe-fff794e40000</link><description>随着伊朗袭击以色列事件尘埃落定，以色列政界人士就以色列应如何应对发出了自己的声音。甘茨和加兰特一致认为，这是结盟对抗伊朗的机会，而以色列极右翼领导人则呼吁在德黑兰市中心进行重大报复</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 19:45:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/opportunity-for-alliance-or-go-berserk-israels-leaders-respond-to-irans-attack/0000018e-ddf7-d7e5-a1fe-fff794e40000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗和以色列距离战争还差一个误判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-14/ty-article/.highlight/iran-and-israel-are-still-one-miscalculation-away-from-war/0000018e-dd89-d7e5-a1fe-ffc9a7e40000</link><description>这场噩梦有很多潜在的触发因素。以乔丹为例，他的处境极其不稳定</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 19:43:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-14/ty-article/.highlight/iran-and-israel-are-still-one-miscalculation-away-from-war/0000018e-dd89-d7e5-a1fe-ffc9a7e40000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击后拜登向以色列传达的信息：趁领先就退出</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/bidens-message-to-israel-after-iran-attack-quit-while-youre-ahead/0000018e-ddc4-d203-a7cf-ffdc8d420000</link><description>在美国竭尽全力帮助以色列成功拦截伊朗的袭击之后，总统现在将目光瞄准了以色列领导人，以避免可能导致该地区全面战争的局势进一步升级，并告诉他们应该抓住这次胜利，并采取行动。继续前行</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 19:00:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/bidens-message-to-israel-after-iran-attack-quit-while-youre-ahead/0000018e-ddc4-d203-a7cf-ffdc8d420000</guid></item><item><title>自杀式无人机、巡航导弹和弹道导弹：伊朗对以色列空袭的详细分析</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/suicide-drones-cruise-and-ballistic-missiles-a-breakdown-of-irans-attack-on-israel/0000018e-dd82-d203-a7cf-ffdee42a0000</link><description>坠落的碎片和照片表明，作为伊朗对以色列领土发动重大袭击的一部分，弹道导弹、GPS制导巡航导弹和带有大型弹头的单向无人机向以色列发射</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 18:17:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/suicide-drones-cruise-and-ballistic-missiles-a-breakdown-of-irans-attack-on-israel/0000018e-dd82-d203-a7cf-ffdee42a0000</guid></item><item><title>幕后花絮：在伊朗大规模袭击期间，美国如何团结起来保卫以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/behind-the-scenes-how-u-s-rallied-to-israels-defense-during-irans-massive-attack/0000018e-dda6-d7e5-a1fe-ffe762960000</link><description>美国官员详细介绍了使用战斗机、军舰、反导系统以及与战略和地区盟友密切沟通与合作拦截伊朗对以色列袭击的协调努力</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 17:45:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-14/ty-article/.premium/behind-the-scenes-how-u-s-rallied-to-israels-defense-during-irans-massive-attack/0000018e-dda6-d7e5-a1fe-ffe762960000</guid></item></channel></rss>